      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.themes.Item.6fZnfXQbv5zr2hLX]{Space Pirate}</p>\n<p>You know how and when to move illicit goods and how to get in and out of tight situations that might spell doom for a less seasoned smuggler. Once per day when you attempt a @Check[type:stealth] to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.5h3iePfJaeQMc3Qr#hide]{hide}, you can roll twice and take the higher result. Additionally, whenever someone attempts a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.gZlg2ZKze0erNLmP]{Perception} check to search your body for objects you have hidden on your person using the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.qVEW9HjXQN0ok879#hide-object]{hide object} task of the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.qVEW9HjXQN0ok879]{Sleight of Hand} skill, the searcher receives only a +2 bonus to the check, instead of a +4 bonus.</p>"
